'''XAT-000 KERYKEION'''

The prototype Advanced Trooper developed by Corusa Industries, the Kerykeion was an experiment in creating an all-purpose humanoid weapon.

''General Specifications''

*All-range combat unit, with a specialty in close combat.
*Battery-operated with an operating time of two hours on a single charge with normal combat activity.
*Capable of jumping up to 200 meters, but incapable of flight.
*One pilot seated in cockpit in upper chest.

''Weapons''

*Four gatling guns mounted two on each wrist.  The weapons are fire-linked for maximum consistency, and are generally designed for use against lightly-armored vehicles and infantry.
*Twin folding blades mounted along the forearms, which flip out for close-combat.  The blades are anti-beam coated to penetrate energy field defenses.

''Armor''

*2-inch Titanitefloalloy armor plating, good for protection against all degrees of small-arms fire and most solid-state ammunition.

